title: Oil Swings as Signs of Oversupply Begin Materializing in Market
description: Oil swung in a choppy trade as investors weighed a price cut on Saudi Arabia’s main grade of crude to Asia, another sign an oversupplied market is weighing on the world’s oil producers even amid considerable geopolitical tensions.
